Package: DAFmap
Type: Package
Title: Direct forest patrols from threats
Version: 1.0
Date: 2017-07-05
Author: Tom Swinfield [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Tom Swinfield <twswinfield@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    maptools,
    rgdal,
    raster,
    ggplot2,
    splancs,
    RColorBrewer,
    rgeos,
    lubridate,
    dplyr,
    rmarkdown,
    tidyr
Description: A tool to integrate forest change alerts from Global
    Land Analysis and Discovery (GLAD) with forest patrol observations
    collected and summarised using the software SMART. Threats are
    summarised within forest patrol sectors, priorities and targets for
    future patrols calculated and patrol performance can be evaluated.
    The software automatically produces an output (currently in Bahasa
    Indonesia).
